{
    "summary": "List __VAR:entity_plural__",
    "description": "Retrieves a paginated list of __VAR:entity_plural__ with support for filtering, sorting, and eager loading of relations.\n\n---\n\n## Model Information\n\n### Available Fields\n__VAR:fields_description__\n\n### Available Relations\n__VAR:relations_description__\n\n---\n\n## Query Parameters\n\n### Pagination\n```json\n{\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"pagesize\": 15\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Loading Relations\nUse dot notation for nested relations.\n```json\n{\n  \"relations\": [\"user\", \"category\", \"user.roles\"]\n}\n```\n\n### Filtering by Attributes\n```json\n{\n  \"attr\": {\n    \"status\": \"active\",\n    \"type\": [\"A\", \"B\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Advanced Filtering (Operators)\nFormat: `operator|field|value|case_sensitive`\n```json\n{\n  \"oper\": [\n    {\n      \"and\": [\n        {\"0\": \"like|name|%search%|0\"},\n        {\"1\": \">|created_at|2024-01-01|0\"}\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n**Operators:** `=`, `!=`, `<`, `>`, `<=`, `>=`,`between`, `like`\n\n### Sorting\n```json\n{\n  \"orderby\": [\n    {\"created_at\": \"desc\"},\n    {\"name\": \"asc\"}\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Field Selection\n```json\n{\n  \"select\": [\"id\", \"name\", \"status\"]\n}\n```",
    "tags": [
        "__VAR:module__"
    ],
    "parameters": [
        {
            "name": "page",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "description": "Page number for pagination",
            "schema": {
                "type": "integer",
                "minimum": 1,
                "default": 1,
                "example": 1
            }
        },
        {
            "name": "pagesize",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "description": "Number of items per page",
            "schema": {
                "type": "integer",
                "minimum": 1,
                "maximum": 100,
                "default": 15,
                "example": 15
            }
        },
        {
            "name": "relations",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "description": "Comma-separated list of relations to load",
            "schema": {
                "type": "string"
            },
            "example": "user,category"
